      "text": [
        " : وَ سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلْحَظِيرَةِ مِنَ اَلْقَصَبِ تُجْعَلُ لِلْحِيتَانِ فِي اَلْمَاءِ فَيَدْخُلُهَا اَلْحِيتَانُ فَيَمُوتُ بَعْضُهَا فِيهَا قَالَ \"لاَ بَأْسَ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4159 - He said: I asked him about an enclosure made of reeds placed in the water for fish, and the fish enter it, and some of them die inside it.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it.\""
        ]
      }
    },
